title: Lena Lorenz
overview: Lena is a midwife with heart and soul, based on the family farm in the Alpine foothills. Besides all the surprises, tragedies and the pure joy the job brings to her and her patients — Lena has to deal with a private life of its own kind: Her mother still tries to cope with her father's tragic death, her grandfather turns everything upside down and on top of all that, Lena tries to keep a stable relationship with Quirin, the love of her life…
